title: Transformers RID 2015 S01E01 720p [TankEngine]
description:
I present to you the first upload of Transformers RID 2015 S01E01 in English! This is the first place and only place I am uploading it. Please feel free to share it around but give credit where credit is due.

Please note that because of the way this is broadcast, it has been upscaled to 720p and so is not "true" 720p.

Video: 

720p @ 50fps (upscaled from 576i @ 25fps)
Encoded w/Apple ProRes 422, H.264

Audio:

MPEG-2 Stereo @ 48kHz
Encoded w/Apple ProRes 422, AAC

Please enjoy this show and make sure to check back later for episode 2 and beyond!
